               <p>THOMAS HARTLEY. I <rs id="t18270913-311-viclabel1734" type="occupation">mend umbrellas</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-311-victim2355 t18270913-311-viclabel1734"></join> in the street. On the 14th of September I was in a skittle-ground near <placeName id="t18270913-311-crimeloc1735">Frederick-street, St. Pancras</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270913-311-crimeloc1735" type="placeName" value="Frederick-street, St. Pancras"></interp>
