                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-311-off1732 t18270913-311-crimeloc1735"></join> - the prisoner was also there - he went away about eight o'clock, and soon afterwards I missed the best umbrella out of my bundle. I followed the prisoner and took him, and found the duplicate of it on him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-311-person2356">
                  DANIEL 
                  SALKELD
               <interp inst="t18270913-311-person2356" type="surname" value="SALKELD"></interp>
