                     <interp inst="t18270913-311-person2356" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was in the skittle-ground, and saw the prisoner take the umbrella from the bundle - I thought he was an acquaintance, but as soon as he got out he ran away with it - we afterwards pursued, and found him with the ticket; the pawnbroker is not here.</p>
